            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Dito Patri et Proserpi<lb break="no" n="2"/>nae <expan><abbr>sacr</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Val</abbr><ex>erius</ex></expan> Zeno <expan><abbr>dec</abbr><ex>urio</ex></expan> et IIvir <expan><abbr>col</abbr><ex>oniae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olvit</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Darstellung von Proserpina, Demeter, Cerberus, Dis Pater und Mercurius. Z. 1/2 oben auf dem Reliefgrund; Z. 3/4 auf dem unteren Reliefrand.</p>
            </div>
